                <zone h='10377' id='33' type-v2='text' w='98688' x='656' y='88868'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='16'>Despite a statistically significant improvement in conversion rates, all ad formats generate negative ROI. Static ads show relatively lower losses compared to video and carousel formats. It is recommended to prioritize static ads while improving cost efficiency and revenue per conversion before scaling overall campaign spend.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
