                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='6349' id='27' type-v2='text' w='98760' x='620' y='16350'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Given consistently negative ROI across all ad formats, budget allocation is optimized to minimize losses rather than maximize returns. Static ads receive the highest allocation due to relatively better efficiency, while carousel ads are significantly reduced. This strategy ensures more effective use of limited budget while highlighting the need to improve unit economics before scaling spend.</run>
